I used to not be able to understand (or at least only sorta understand) too.  Then I joined the guild I'm in. 
<br />

<br />
Yes, this is a very good weapon, but it's likely to end up in a bag when it should be EPIC, not directly comparable to stuff you have/can get when you are able to complete the quest.   This is supposed to be the ultimate bard item (for a few expansions at least), and it should reflect that. 
<br />

<br />
<blockquote><b>Quote:</b><br><span class="quote">1) Mod to all intruments and singing. 
<br />
-I have fairly decent gear, and yet still many of my mods would improve with this item </span></blockquote> 
