I have fairly decent gear too.  My low mod is 2.2 (wind), and the rest are 2.4 or 2.5.  I will have 2.7-2.9 gear available to me, by the time I can get the globe, with an almost guarentee of 2.6 for most everything.  
<br />

<br />
A 2.7 mod vs a 2.5 or 2.6 mod is negligible, and no reason to use this above anything else. 
<br />

<br />
It should have a mod equal to (or possible a tiny bit higher) than anything else we have available.  Hence my suggestion for a 2.9 or 3.0 mod on it. 
<br />

