<blockquote><b>Quote:</b><br><span class="quote">3) One of, if not THE best weapon ratios in the game for bards. </span></blockquote> 
<br />

<br />
The ratio is 34/22, which is a 1.54 ratio.  The magic damage, which is not always going to be effective, brings it to a 1.63 ratio.  
<br />

<br />
There's weapons with ratio's like 33/22 and 32/21 available to bards by the time they can get here.  And there will probably be other things with ratios about as good. 
<br />

<br />
The change I suggest (making it 36/22 with +2 magic) would put it just below the ranger epic for ratio.  And make it very much worth using. 
<br />

<br />
