				<td colspan="2"><span>I see a couple posts saying this would be a great item for them because they are elemental/time leavel geared. <b>Epic 2.0 REQUIRES anguish access.</b> How much of an upgarde will this be when you have access to anguish level gear? Surprisingly not as much as you would think. Really the ones saying it needs aa boost are capable of getting this item, the ones saying its great are strutting around in gear 2 expansions old (yah, ldon doesn't count).
