				<td colspan="2"><span>Madon is so right about how we have been nerfed worse that we realize. Our epics are great if you are in a low level guild but if you are in a guild capable of easily acquiring them they are going straight into your bag. Our epic 1.0 lasted for many expansions but these are marginal upgrades on inception. Our other nerfs?
<br />

<br />
    Soloability. We cant swarm or AE for any real exp or loot anymore. We can chant kite mobs with lots of HP if they dont summon. Ok maybe we werent meant to solo.
<br />

<br />
     Songs. In MPG my cleric sent me a tel asking me to play something more useful than the mana song. With c6 and a bst in the group plus his full mana regen and large mana pool the song was irrelevant. The regen component? Everyone in the group cept me had over 10k HP so really what was the point? So, out of our 20 runes or so the ueful ones are the attack song,overhaste and the new mezzes. This actually beating a dead horse as this has been gone over before but I was truly surprised about the mana song thing. After years of getting into groups just because they wanted the mana song we no longer have that as a draw sometimes.
<br />

<br />
      Pulling. Monks and rangers have new AA's, skills, spells so ew are hardly the supreme pullers anymore (if we ever were). As a side note I beleive they (SOE) have been slowly pushing the pulling chores back to the FD classes anyway. When OOW came out the higher level zones had mobs that our more effective pulling tools (mez especially) did not work on. You needed the songs from those zones to be able to play in those zones. FD, a low level skill worked right away.
<br />

<br />
     Resists. The trend here seems to be a reliance on group healing classes to handle the AE,s  rather than increasing resists to avoid them. 
<br />

<br />
     DPS. Seems we are just as or maybe even more behind. Now   2 of the 3 best melee dps classes can pull as well or better than we can. Anyone see rogues getting mez and snare soon? 
<br />

<br />
     CC. Almost everything at higher levels needs to be debuffed to mez now. So if you need to do real CC hard to lock down even 2 reliably. Yes, I know when grouping most zones dont require much CC but if things do go bad not much chance you can pull things out.
<br />

<br />
    Still, I would miss playing the bard and as our server loses players our general utility saves us. However, I certainly dont stay on very long anymore if no group is forthcoming. Chant kiting for AA just sux.
<br />

<br />
Rinludar
